Package: GeneSummary
Type: Package
Title: RefSeq Gene Summaries
Version: 0.99.2
Date: 2021-09-03
Authors@R: person("Zuguang", "Gu", email = "z.gu@dkfz.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c('ORCID'="0000-0002-7395-8709"))
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, markdown, testthat
biocViews: AnnotationData, Organism, Homo_sapiens
Description: This package provides long description of genes collected from 
    the RefSeq database. The text in "COMMENT" section started with "Summary"
    is extracted as the description of the gene. The long text descriptions
    can be used for analysis such as text mining.
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/jokergoo/GeneSummary
BugReports: https://github.com/jokergoo/GeneSummary/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
NeedsCompilation: no
